Rootfs overlay for Raspberry Pi 4

This directory structure will be copied over the target filesystem during the build.
Any files placed here will override or be added to the target rootfs.

Examples:
- /etc/motd - Customize the message of the day
- /etc/hostname - Set the hostname
- /etc/network/interfaces - Custom network configuration
- /usr/bin/custom-script.sh - Add custom scripts
- /etc/systemd/system/*.service - Add systemd services

